data.description: Original 3/2 spacious home in popular North Andrews Gardens, offers GREAT POTENTIAL with many upgraded features already included… IMPACT windows/doors throughout, Florida room, recent new roof and new AC, ceramic tile flooring everywhere (Terrazzo underneath), updated GRANITE kitchen with high end cabinetry, updated bathrooms with GRANITE, NATURAL GAS TANKLESS water heater, full home GENERATOR on natural gas (never run out), sprinkler system and storage room. PRIVATE ENTRANCE to 3rd BEDROOM AND BATH provides possible FUTURE RENTAL OPTION. The large covered patio includes structural footings for possible future expansion. NO restrictions & NO HOA ~ Great location EAST of I-95 ~ very walkable to grocery, pharmacy, restaurants and other shopping ~ near to famous Wilton Manors and the beach!
